Can COVID-19 vaccine make me sick with COVID-19? 
NO - none of authorised/recommended COVID-19 vaccines contain the live virus that causes COVID-19. This means that a COVID-19 vaccine cannot make you sick with COVID-19. Src:CDC #CHIVASouthAfrica #CHIVAAfrica #vaccine #COVID19 https://t.co/2QhARJiN8H
